<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1437,153,972]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,463,225,251]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Variation in plumage.</emphasis>
Most specimens show pale streaking in the centers of some contour feathers, and in some the intensity of breast feathers suggests a diffuse band.
</paragraph>
